Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The more Benio read the first letter she'd gotten from Shinobu, the more her feelings overflowed.{"had got" = British, "had gotten" = American}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, how sweet, yet sorrowful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But just when she sat down and tried responding to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,she ended up falling into the arms of Morpheus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Shinobu once again fell victim to Innen's plotting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and found himself in a platoon full of rogues,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who waste no time in starting a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The garrison commander \Nsoon realizes what's happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and immediately confronts Shinobu \Nto know the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shinobu says the truth, he'll be safe, while Onijima will be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he going to do in this Siberian do-or-die situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:03.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE4E0E1&\bord0\blur1.001\pos(763,137)}Episode 28 {\fs79.999}\NA Battle for Men, a Battle for Women
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Second Lieutenant Ijuuin! \NI want to know what the cause of the brawl was!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What you saw was not a brawl, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to be ready for upcoming battles, so we decided to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, things are going differently \Nfrom what I'd expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're always here, \Nwe've long been itching for some action.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, training for real combat, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a brawl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. If you guys are craving action that much, \Nthen I'll grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your unit is getting transferred to the front line in the nearest future!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Front line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Front line?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better be ready to get moving! Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To the front line...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry this is what it came to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! We'll follow Second Lieutenant to the depths of Hell or wherever else he goes, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Platoon commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're to blame for getting the wrong idea about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When we heard that a Tokyo officer would take the lead here, we thought we were being made fun of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,However, because I spoke too much, I ended up sending us all to the front line. {Original translation was way too clunky}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? Besides, it's true that we're itching to get some action.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I, the unworthy{不肖} Sergeant Onijima, will always be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're with you, commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.07,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not backing off either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll follow you anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys... Everyone got themselves a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{Platoon}Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon. You need to get wasted too. Wasted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This sure feels good!\NLet's celebrate the eve of our departure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll finally get to show the world what outcast rogues like us are capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. Wherever I go, I end up getting entangled with heavy drinkers, be it Benio or this platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, that fight we had today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whichever way you look at it, \Nit was Benio's style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the front line tomorrow... \NBut I'll come home safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, I'll always find my way back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us have a sip.{ご相伴します}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was truly delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to force yourself, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, this is still nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Shinobu is out there fighting on the battlefield, behaving like a proper wife is the least I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And, in the meantime, I'll become so beautiful that he won't believe his eyes when he sees me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have turned so ladylike by the time he returns home safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitsch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become more and more ladylike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I've once again beheaded a flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... She'll never learn, it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NYou can't breathe because of your face mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be ladylike... Ladylike...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1918, young noble girls used to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,nursery rhymes such as "The Canary's Song" and "The Drummer Raccoons' Song".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The canary forgot its songs!! {https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NlPd0geh6Xw&ab_channel=MountNeko}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was this noise? \NIt broke the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that just now?\NHuh? Just a children's song? {童謡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a cat getting strangled to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, Benio sure has changed so much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where her old self has gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all for love... \NIt's for Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So now you're {\i1}that{\i0} \Nhead over heels for him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, never! I just can't accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Keep your cool, Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She leaves me no choice but to lead an okama's{/transvestite's} life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What should I do, Ushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, I'll poke my eyes too. {probably means "I won't be able to see you as an okama" but maybe "you're making me uncomfortable [by hanging on me]"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A ball?{In Japanese she mistakes budou for grape-picking}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just received an invitation, \Nso you might as well go entertain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We all need a change of pace every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:29.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.419122\fscx81.039\fscy125.28\frz-5.4619\frx5.4363\fry-11.9280\xbord1.4\ybord1.01\blur1.001\org(1062,707)\pos(1070.78,675.36)\c&H23268E&}A letter of invitation {御招待状}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we want you to have more experiences,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and get to know all about the world of the nobles \Nwhile you wait for Shinobu to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely. This will be your classy debut to the high society. I'll accompany you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that makes sense.\NThe weather is looking to be just right. {lit: It's already autumn, after all. - benio still thinking it's about grapes}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing ball sounds like a wonderful idea.{lit: grapes should be tasty just about now}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I last played ball.{/Maybe I could invite my friends to play ball too. - perevodildo}{lit: It's been a while since I went grape picking.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, this looks so good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,back in the day, this was my go-to choice when I had to dress up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Count. Shall we go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh! Ow-ow-ow-ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we'll be alright...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're now headed to the ballroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hip hip hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but wonder whether Benio will do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about those two \Ngoing out on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit worried too. \NI can get you there if you wanna follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, now let's see what I can come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're setting off! Now floor it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, all the soldiers of the Ijuuin platoon are being deployed to the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers, attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To your left!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,March forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for them - \Nthey're going to the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if any of them will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. It's a motley crew of scoundrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's gonna miss them \Neven if they all get wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, is it Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as per your request, Second Lieutenant Ijuuin's unit has just departed for the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied now, Lieutenant Colonel​?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be sure, you sent them to the Siberian front line, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just the front line, it's straight up Hell out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's ever made it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid. Splendid. Just splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? They're dancing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So chic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on your own now, okay, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, Ushi. \NNoble gatherings are my forte! {social life; social intercourse}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that back in the Meiji era \Nit was even more lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right, Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These dances look pretty different from the loach-catching ones.{https://youtu.be/mUALuGno6Go}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me, count.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're saying is that \Nthis is your first ever ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Called it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I forced myself to wear a dress like this in order to appear more ladylike...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is a pain to walk in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Ah... B-B-Benio! \NYour legs! Your legs are bare!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you just need to bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu... I'll be doing my best \Nuntil the day you come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is everybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First squad: no one missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Second squad: everybody's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Third squad... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're missing one! \NPrivate Kobayashi isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sergeant Onijima, \Ntake command of the platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi! Private Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi, where are you?! \NPrivate Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Private Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hang in there! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There, please stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Commander, please leave without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're exhausted and alone here, \Nyou'll be dead in no time! {no clue what he means: if exhausted here, your pride's tattoo will be gone}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot walk any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a fever for two days already...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me? I would've let you stay in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never stand still when all my buddies are out there facing death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a family waiting for you back home, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite. I've always been an orphan. There's no one waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be someone, at least one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, \Nback when I was in reform school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a teacher who was really kind to me.{I'll assume that it's a man they're talking about, since it happened in a juvenile colony}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to meet him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I can guarantee you that he's waiting for your safe return to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for him that you have to stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There. There, let's get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hop on the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Onijima...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi's my friend, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't stand still.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Onijima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to take command in my stead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember acknowledging \Nthat command, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, it's unsafe to stay \Nin a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Onijima, hop on the horse and take Kobayashi to safety. Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is an order from your superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter who's the superior out here.{"whose" was correct as far as I know, but I feel that in the way people actually speak, it's not natural outside the start of a question as in "whose commander is this?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfair that only one gets \Nto ride in the saddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree, commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you tell me then—what’s your draw method of choice? {lit: what is your specialty gambling - as in "how would you prefer to decide it"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Let's use them to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, roll them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with odds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I bet on the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, ready now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is odd, right? Or is it even?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk, would you look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it sure feels bad to lose to a beginner who doesn't even know the difference between odd and even.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And... up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, don't become the wolves' dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, to decide my own fate... \NShould I go with even or odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, it's you, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Tamaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world did you \Nend up in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of my diverse training program.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Training?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see. It's something you're going to do until Shinobu returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you really shouldn't have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in here is staring at you with contempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Contempt? Huh, why? What'd I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what you did, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu was the idol of this high society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Among both young and adult noble women,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,there isn't anyone who hasn't fallen for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, there's no shortage of women \Nwho would've loved to marry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you must know that they aren't as noble when it comes to words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll be able to endure that pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, would you take a look at who \Nthe missy Tamaki is talking to, madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic! It looks like she chose an antiquated dress for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know, \Nshe must be but a country bumpkin.{maybe the right level of fancy?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Look, that's her. \NThe girl that came with Count Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Shinobu's betrothed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So that girl is his fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've expected her to be astoundingly beautiful in order to match Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous, I'm way prettier than her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Our dear lady-killer Shinobu sure has a fancy taste in women, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that’s fine too. How should we punish her for getting ahead of us and stealing our Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's walk up to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's give her a warm welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I see it now, \Neveryone is staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Count Ijuuin! What a truly rare sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I just wanted to introduce my granddaughter to the high class tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you know, \Nwe were talking about her just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't help but notice \Nwhat a gorgeous and refined lady she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have guts, I heard everything you said about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this juice is so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't this champagne?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! \NEven if it's a refined alcohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio will go into a frenzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just juice, so I can drink however much I want, right? Hic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, B-Benio, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just at the right time, Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get me something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right after I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, darn, I've lost sight of my platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just me, Second Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's you, Onijima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I got Kobayashi to safety. Now, get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you ended up in a wolf's belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I? \NEven dogs wouldn't want to eat me. {literal, dunno waht he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have your precious dices back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant, I'd like you to keep them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll bring you good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Having them saves you from illness and misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If they have such capabilities, you should be the one keeping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep them, Second Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:21:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance! You take them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'll follow you \Nto the bitter end, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant, we've got company.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So we're surrounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Albeit unknowingly, \NBenio broke her oath of abstinence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Might this attract the gods' fury and bring calamity on Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do now, High Collar Lady?\N The night takes hold for both of you. {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:54.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,Next episode preview
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.21,0:22:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu and Onijima are surrounded by a large enemy force.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this have been caused by Benio, who broke her oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the hostile land of Siberia, what fate will Shinobu face?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Benio is doing Benio things{not sure about 進軍ラッパ - might be metaphorical to compare her situation to Shinobu's?; no idea here either, literally "march trumpet" - means "forward unit" or something to that extent}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and her wild drunken side \Nbrings chaos to the ballroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.57,0:23:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Here Comes the High Collar Lady: \NIn the Thick of the Siberian Battle. {硝煙弾雨のシベリアで}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:21.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 29\NIn the Thick of the Siberian Battle {硝煙弾雨のシベリアで}
Comment: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED start}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,20,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
